From: Bastian Germann <bage@debian.org>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 23:30:30 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Prevent generating script

Even with calling qt-generate-deploy-app-script with the right syntax,
we do not want the library bundle on Debian.
---
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -88,10 +88,3 @@ install(TARGETS cen64-qt
     BUNDLE DESTINATION .
     RUNTIME DESTINATION ${CMAKE_INSTALL_BINDIR}
 )
-
-qt_generate_deploy_app_script(
-    TARGET cen64-qt
-    FILENAME_VARIABLE deploy_script
-    NO_UNSUPPORTED_PLATFORM_ERROR
-)
-install(SCRIPT ${deploy_script})
